content: My unit, 125th FA, was based in Pine City, Minnesota. I lived in Harris, MN. when I joined in '76, attended North Branch HS '73-'74, and one day in '76 and Pine City HS in '74-'75. Also lived previously on Rush Lake and attended school in Braham, MN '71-'72. I have also lived in both St. Paul and Mpls., attended Lincoln Elementary and South St. Paul Junior High and Inver Hills Community College, class of '83. Spent many summers on Big Marine Lake, too.
